             was indicted for <rs id="t18010218-1-off1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18010218-1-off1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010218-1-off1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18010218-1-cd2" type="crimeDate">24th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010218-1-off1 t18010218-1-cd2"></join>, a pair of drab cloth breeches, value 12s. a swansdown waistcoat, value 8s. and a cloth great coat, value 21s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18010218-1-victim3" type="victimName">
                        Richard 
                        Angel
                     <interp inst="t18010218-1-victim3" type="surname" value="Angel"></interp>
